items.label: Returning To The Uk
items.summary: The Duke and Duchess of Sussex have been asked to vacate their residence at Rockmore Cottage. Jiahe, Yooni, DAZHI and others are meeting today.

items.label: Guilty Verdict
items.summary: Marty Murdoch was convicted on Thursday of murdering his wife and son. The minimum sentence for the crime is 30 years in prison. His lawyer is Per. Mardo was found guilty of 2 counts of possession of a weapon doing the commission of a violent crime.

items.label: Data Centers
items.summary: Yooni and Jiahe discuss the evolution of data center design and the development of cloud computing. Yooni is looking for a job for the summer.
